skimage读取彩色图片并显示¶

In [ ]:
from skimage import data,io
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np


legacy_datasets = [
    'astronaut.png',
    'brick.png',
    'camera.png',
    'chelsea.png',
    'coffee.png',
    'coins.png',
    'cell.png',
    'grass.png',
    'gravel.png',
    'horse.png',
    'hubble_deep_field.jpg',
    'logo.png',
    'microaneurysms.png',
    'moon.png',
    'page.png',
    'text.png',
    'retina.jpg',
    'rocket.jpg',
]

path_of_images = data.data_dir
print(len(legacy_datasets))

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(16,9))
i=1

for each in legacy_datasets:
    path = data.data_dir + "\{}".format(each )
    img_ = io.imread(path)

    sub = fig.add_subplot(3,6,i)
    if img_.ndim > 2 :
        sub.imshow(img_)
    else:
        sub.imshow(img_, cmap='gray')

    i = i+1

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
